data.description: 3 Bed 1.5 Bath home in a really nice part of Big Bear city on a well treed corner lot. One of the bedrooms is a separate unit that would make a nice guest house or even a game room. It has an upgraded kitchen, new dual pane windows, and vintage wood floors and walls in the living room and bedrooms in the house.
